  m_text: 'The S and Z pieces can rotate around an overhang.


    For the S piece,
    rotate it cw to set it up, then cw again to rotate it around the overhang.


    For
    the Z piece, rotate it ccw to set it up, then ccw again to rotate it around the
    overhang.


    Note: The shapes might look the same if you rotate them cw or
    ccw but they won''t rotate in unless they are oriented properly.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6af94fbdd2e124181a1892a853cdf440, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -2504890859898317026, guid: 6af94fbdd2e124181a1892a853cdf440, type: 2}
