  m_text: "When doing T-spins we saw that the T-piece could rotate in unexpected
    ways. \n\nModern Tetris has some interesting rotation mechanics called the Super
    Rotation System, or SRS.\n\nAll the pieces except the O piece have special rotation
    mechanics. \n\nKnowing them can help if you're not sure what to do with a piece!\n\nLet's
    explore them!"
